title: George Clinton (Part 2)
itunes:title: George Clinton (Part 2)
description:
And the ride on the mothership continues! This week we dive into part 2 of Questlove Supreme’s interview with the legendary George Clinton. This episode hits all the topics you thought we missed and asks the questions you’ve been waiting to hear the answers to. From Zapp to Prince and all things in between, make sure you complete your ride on the mothership with Questlove Supreme.
